Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. One Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where is my red cherry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to have a red cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or you can't call this a Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta pay more attention next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Business is better when I have\Nthis in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my superstition. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,VERDEN (GERMANY)\NSPRINGER MANSION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let there be some valuables left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, looking good. Just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept everything as is.\NI can just take my pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's see if there is anything\Nworthy of the great Heckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Life sure is short, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're running for state governor,\Nit's meaningless when you're shot dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, back to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I saw the safe\Nsomewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That gave me the chills.\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had this bad feeling before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I freaked out? This is not like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he was behind me? Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all because that bartender\Nforgot my red cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey officer, can you cut me some slack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, so you're\Nin my line of business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about you put\Nthat dangerous thing down and calmly--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with this guy?\NHe seems to be worse than the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A screwup like you will only slow me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! What an unlucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you looked familiar.\NYou're the doctor on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the material witness\Nin Congressman Springer's murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you,\NI don't do anything as crude as murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about the incident\Nthat happened in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows. Anyway, just get lost already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you were\Na top-notch surgeon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got an idea in my brilliant brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think people meet only\Nby coincidence, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.\NThere's always a reason that people meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are meant to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In the underworld, there are many people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,who are in need of someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,People who die
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's too dangerous\Nto call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let good old Heckel\Ntake care of the management.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you the world's best\Nunderworld doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to earn so much more\Nin the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be a billionaire in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He… Hey, doctor! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know\Nabout the murder in that mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did see the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you mean?\N-You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the killer a blond man\Naround 20 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me everything\Nyou know about the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only tell you if you team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the third floor of this tenement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I researched that congressman's mansion\Nfor a month after I set my eyes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I decided to do the job,\Nthe guy showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked into the window,\Nand I saw the Springers' dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd follow the killer\Nand shake him down for some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your innocence has now been proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell the police\Nor do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we can have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk about\Nour bright future together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He… Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, meeting him?\NHe's a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! What the hell is he thinking?\NUnbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But such a money tree\Ndoesn't come by often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My policy is never to cross\Nany dangerous bridges.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another hot day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doctor. Are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? He's got a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to take walks with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd walk down the road by a sunflower\Nfield on summer days like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you asked by someone to use that gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A man…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. One day, he spoke to me at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A young blond man about 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Erich had such a beautiful smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Erich this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We became friends after meeting\Nseveral times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He invited me to his house, \NCongressman Springer's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he live in that house until recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Springers treated him\Nlike their son since a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched that house for a month,\Nbut I didn't see anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They were a beautiful family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a photo of me\Nand the congressman's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just couldn't forgive\Nthem for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a sunflower garden\Nin their property.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The congressman destroyed it\Nto make room for parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said that it was terrible of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Erich agreed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that you killed him\Njust because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Erich told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Congressman Springer had a mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "I don't want to be in\NCongressman Springer's family anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am not a part of this family."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he asked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to "erase this family."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was horrible of him to have a mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was someone's mistress as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Well. Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where the safe is\Nin that mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's in the back of the study\Non the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,O… Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. You should get out\Nof here soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that you can erase your past?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like your past,\Nyou can just erase everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reset your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One can try to forget the past,\Nbut one cannot erase the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what got into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I think I could erase the past\Nby pulling the trigger then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I listen to his request?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I have to say. Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Tenma, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read the message.\NIt's from him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the study of the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew that you would be coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Erich told me himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He said,\N"your fate has already been decided."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I told you--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you actually…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you die, everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to stay alive.\NIsn't that right, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You do make good points\Nevery so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:12:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're tracking down this Johan,\Na dangerous serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you forget about that\Nabsurd thing and team up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, when I was about to open\Nthe door to this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt this chill in my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trembling, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me, look at me."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is how big the monster\Ninside me has grown, Dr. Tenma."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan… He's enjoying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me. Hey, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something good for you.\NYou should thank me for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you promise to team up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I was going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You need money to be hiding\Nfrom the police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your client.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He will take you to the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep your things for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want them back,\Ndo the job and get the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to Frank's place in Graschten Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Later. Go and get me some good money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This business is a sweet deal for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the advance money already,\Nso maybe I'll get a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawyer, I brought the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NDoctor, hurry and stop my bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An artery in your armpit has been damaged.\NWere you shot by a shotgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the doctor doesn't\Nhave anything with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get the surgical equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… No. It's a mess out there.\NI didn't get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we have the equipment,\NI can't do the surgery here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You should let him go to a real doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We would've done that already if we could!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How long ago was he shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it four hours ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You committed\Nthis morning's terror attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if that was us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't treat people who commit\Nrandom terror attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what situation\Nyou're in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, our buddies will be coming\Nto help us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop my bleeding until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But… Lawyer…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, my life is\Nin this doctor's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die, you can shoot him dead then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not running a charity over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you pay us back\Nthe 250 thousand marks, Heckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gross, I do intend to pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.\NJust that thought alone makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just break both of his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! I'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give me one more month!\N-News on the shootings…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then break both of his legs.\N-…in Erfurt this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From the eyewitness testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the suspects were identified\Nas Max Steindorf and Karl Brandt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The GWE is offering 300 thousand marks
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as a reward for any helpful tips\Nabout these two suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where those guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can forget about the debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling the truth?\NIf not, I will break your neck, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious! I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but Tenma is over there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said what I did\Nwas a random terror attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did was for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to kill the chairman of GWE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so good now\Nthat I can die anytime now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a lawyer in East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was a politician's secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the wall came down,\Nwe all lost our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, can you understand how we feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after the wall collapsed,\Nthe GWE invaded the east
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and did whatever they wanted\Nwith their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They built factories by force\Non our lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot that guy with pride\Nin my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pride…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!\NOur buddies will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that they are not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bleeding, now!\NIf not… I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die… No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared? Scared of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They all felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the 12 people you killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it means to kill people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me disinfectant and scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have those, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an arterial hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going into shock\Nfrom low blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop the bleeding by pressing\Non the arteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need a needle and thread\Nto sew up the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get me a stapler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A… A stapler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry up and get me one!\N-Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I did first aid,\Nso now I'll take him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho… Hospital? What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Put him down, or I'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you shoot me,\Nyou have to take this man to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you looked familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that doctor who's wanted\Nfor serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did wasn't a random terror attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The people I killed were
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the chairman of GWE,\Nand his flunkies and bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're saying that nobody\Ngot caught in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean that kid in the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew that you shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because you're afraid\Nof being killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes aren't those of someone\Nwho's afraid of being shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save the killer who\Ncommitted a random terror attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe you're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and go! The police are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an excellent doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what happened to the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you just treated him\Nand came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrorist suspects\Nhave been apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just say something!\N-A struggle was expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but they surrendered quickly\Nwithout resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not running a charity here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
